description:
These are simply too good not to share --

Globally-renown needle-dropper PBTHAL's two definitive Megadeth vinyl rips of  two all-time classic titles -- &quot;Countdown To Extinction&quot; (1992) and &quot;Youtnanasia&quot; (1994).

Quite simply, *** THESE ARE THE BEST SOUNDING VERSIONS OF THESE TWO CLASSICS OUT THERE.***  They blow the MFSL editions and 2004 Remasters away.  It's not even close.  One listen will make that abundantly clear.  Way more Dynamic Range (DR) and NO BRICKWALLING.  

So enjoy and PLAY LOUD!  And don't forget to thank the mighty PBTHAL for insuring these albums were heard the way they were intended to -- despite the record label's best efforts.

